---
layout: layout.njk
title: Blog
description: Practical articles on construction management, scheduling, budgets, and getting the most out of SSI Construction Manager.
---

<div class="mb-10">
  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Blog</p>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Insights for builders & construction managers</h1>
  <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl">
    Hands-on guides on construction scheduling, budgeting, change control, and using SSI Construction Manager to keep projects on time and on budget.
  </p>
</div>

<ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
  {% set posts = collections.posts | reverse %}
  {% for post in posts %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}"
         class="block h-full p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-300 transition">
        {% if post.data.category %}
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">{{ post.data.category }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 leading-snug mb-2">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        {% if post.data.description %}
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 line-clamp-3">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-500">{{ post.date | postDate }}</p>
      </a>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
